The taste is exceptionally sweet on the first sip, then it evaporates into a
completely vapid flavor, devoid of anything but its sweetener components. It's
exceptionally artificial and scarcely reminds of of Red Bull at all. The sour
apple taste of [[the OG|Red_Bull]] is just not there. Even Red Bull Sugar Free
is more enjoyable to me and more redolent of the king.

